## Show (Task Pane)

> Example:

```vb
Dim bResult As Boolean
bResult = Reporting.TaskPane.IsVisible()
If bResult = True Then
Call Reporting.TaskPane.Show()
End If
```

You can use the Show method to reveal the Task Pane in your report. To use the Show method, there must be an active connection to a TM1 server via the API or the Planning Analytics for Microsoft Excel login.

### Syntax

The following is the syntax for the Show method.

`Reporting.TaskPane.Show()`


